msgid ""
"<<{baseurl}/truck-description-file/index.adoc#wheels2,Wheels2>> (also known "
"as the \"complex wheel model\") allows you to separate the wheel [rim] from "
"the tire. This requires extra syntax, namely specifying the characteristics "
"of the wheel versus the tire. Traditionally the wheel will be very rigid "
"with the tire being much less so. The rigidity of wheels2 tires can be "
"altered by holding [ and ] ingame, resulting in this:"
