#. type: Plain text
#: content/source/docs/rorbook/index.adoc:463
msgid ""
"This section allows you to define a torque curve for your vehicle. It is "
"optional."
msgstr ""

#. type: Plain text
#: content/source/docs/rorbook/index.adoc:465
msgid ""
"This allows you to assign predefined torque curves or your own custom curves "
"to a truck. Predefined options are: `default`, `diesel`, `turbodiesel`, "
"`gas`, `turbogas`, `wheelloader`, `compacttractor`, `tractor`, `hydrostatic`."
msgstr ""

#. type: Plain text
#: content/source/docs/rorbook/index.adoc:467
