#. type: Plain text
#: content/source/docs/rorbook/index.adoc:612
msgid ""
"The swing axle is a small step up from the beam axle. Although it is the "
"most common form of suspension on Pricorde's trucks, it probably produces "
"the worst handling vehicles in the game, due to the way the camber changes "
"when going over bumps."
